Subject: Your [interview_stage] for [job_title] at Outsourced Pro Global!

Body:
<html><body style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #222222; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; padding: 0;">
<p style="margin: 0 0 14px 0;">Hi <strong>[applicant_first_name]</strong>,</p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 14px 0;">Thank you for your interest in joining <strong>Outsourced Pro Global</strong>. We're excited to let you know that your profile has been shortlisted, and you're moving on to the next step in our hiring process.</p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 14px 0;"><strong>[hiring_manager_name], our [position_title],</strong> will meet with you via Zoom.</p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 14px 0;">The applicant's resume is attached to this email.</p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 8px 0;"><strong>Interview details:</strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0 0 14px 0; padding: 12px 16px; background-color: #f5f5f5; border-left: 3px solid #cccccc; line-height: 2;">
  <strong>Date:</strong> [Date]<br>
  <strong>Time:</strong> [Time] [Timezone]<br>
  <strong>Platform:</strong> Zoom<br>
  <strong>Zoom Link:</strong> <a href="[Link]">[Link]</a>
</p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 8px 0;"><strong>Meeting guests:</strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0 0 14px 0; line-height: 1.8;">[guest_list_text]</p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 8px 0;"><strong>Friendly Reminders:</strong></p>

<ul style="margin: 0 0 14px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
<li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Kindly connect 10 minutes early to make sure your camera and microphone are working properly.</li>
<li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Use your laptop or PC for this interview.</li>
<li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Make sure that your <strong>Full Name</strong> and the <strong>role</strong> you are interviewing for are reflected in the Zoom meeting.</li>
<li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Please note that this is a formal meeting - please dress in business attire.</li>
<li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">If you have any questions, feel free to reach out to any of our recruiters at <strong>+61 489 275 966 (AU)</strong> or contact your recruiter at <strong>[recruiter_phone_line]</strong>.</li>
</ul>

<p style="margin: 0 0 4px 0;">Warm regards,</p>
<p style="margin: 0 0 14px 0;">Recruitment Team, Outsourced Pro Global</p>

[signature]
